metadata.name: Page 1: Notre-Dame Blues
metadata.description:
The God Forsaken collection is a series of quick, almost gestural animated sketches, that try to capture the quiet sadness of life in the big cities. 

Notre-Dame Blues tells a very common story that we have seen so often we don’t even care anymore. 

Music: “Radio Trumpet”, by MindFreeMedia, licensed from Envato.
